import { Col, Row } from "react-bootstrap";

import style from "./css/matchOPPO/MatchOPPO.module.css";

const MatchOPPO = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Row className={style["background"]}>
        <Row className={style["contentBody"]}>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Row>HOME</Row>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Row>AWAY</Row>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Row>팀 로고</Row>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Row>VS</Row>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Row>팀 로고</Row>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Row>팀 이름</Row>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Row>팀 이름</Row>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Row>팀 전적</Row>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Row>팀 전적</Row>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Row>
                <Row>선발 투수 헤드</Row>
                <Row>선발 투수 바디</Row>
              </Row>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Row>
                <Row>선발 투수 헤드</Row>
                <Row>선발 투수 바디</Row>
              </Row>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Row>
      </Row>
    </>
  );
};

export default MatchOPPO;
